Police say a postmortem will be conducted to determine the cause of death.CAPE TOWN Cape Town police were called to the scene where the body of a child has been found.The body was found near the N2 Highway in Strand, EWN reported.This comes on the last day of the annual child protection week.The police&#8217;s Frederick van Wyk says, We can confirm that the body of a child was found this afternoon, in Nomzamo in Strand. A postmortem will be conducted to determine the cause of death. Source: EWN